法規內容.條文內容:
Level 1 prisoners should be placed in special sections and entitled to the following privileges:
1. Living quarters with unlocked doors;
2. No extra monitoring surveillance;
3. Permission for conjugal time with spouse and sharing time with direct kin within designated quarters and periods;
The enforcement rules of the three subparagraphs of the preceding paragraph are subject to the discretion of the Ministry of Justice.
